content.text: WHAT do you get when you cross the circus with the Port of Echuca ? The answer is Poppy Fairbairn and Zion Martyn from The Uncaged Spirit Circus Club , based in Moama . The pair were busy entertaining the tourism precinct during the recent school holidays . And council 's economic and community development general manager Keith Oberin said that was n't all on in the area . '' There 's been plenty on for tourists and locals at Echuca 's port precinct , '' he said . '' The last weekend of the holidays was a great one with yoga , small engine club displays , interactive circus activities , animal nursery and live music . ''
